      <description>Yup it really does&amp;#8230; Hey there it&amp;#8217;s Sven. Enticing title, isn&amp;#8217;t it? Most of us connect education with school, you know that boring place that feels like ages ago but still it&amp;#8217;s fresh in mind that education was boring. Well, it doesn&amp;#8217;t have to be and certainly it is something we need. Now, I&amp;#8217;m not [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/sven-wolf-a-becoming-entrepreneur/Sven_Wolf_-_a_becoming_entrepreneur-So_Education_and_Achieving_Goals_Walk_Hand_in_Hand.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Yup it really does&#8230;</p>
<p>Hey there it&#8217;s Sven.</p>
<p>Enticing title, isn&#8217;t it? Most of us connect education with school, you know that boring place that feels like ages ago but still it&#8217;s fresh in mind that education was boring.</p>
<p>Well, it doesn&#8217;t have to be and certainly it is something we need.</p>
<p>Now, I&#8217;m not talking math and all that (unless it is part of your goals) I&#8217;m talking info about stuff you need to know.</p>
<p>If you want to market on the internet for example. You need to educate yourself on marketing on the internet. If you want to build websites you need to edcate yourself on that. Yup, education.</p>
<p>No go write down what you need to educate yourself on and get started.</p>
<p>I found this video I made a while ago and I felt that this is as important now as it was back then.</p>
<p>Here it is. Please leave your comments below.<br />
<br ><br />
<center><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zng6GYOHFDw?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br />
<br ></p>
<p>Take care</p>
