      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://whoissvenwolf.com/?p=1072</guid>
      <description>Hey there! So, in the last couple of weeks I have gotten more response than ever. What seems to be the regular type of questions is how to achieve goals financially. Now, I haven&amp;#8217;t really focused that much on this topic simply because I believe that happiness and abundance must come first. But of course [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/sven-wolf-a-becoming-entrepreneur/Sven_Wolf_-_a_becoming_entrepreneur-Achieving_Goals__Financial_Goals.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hey there!</p>
<p>So, in the last couple of weeks I have gotten more response than ever.</p>
<p>What seems to be the regular type of questions is how to achieve goals financially.<br />
<br ><br />
<center><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PWeNufUzH3Q?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br />
<br ><br />
Now, I haven&#8217;t really focused that much on this topic simply because I believe that happiness and abundance must come first. But of course I will direct these a little more on economy and how to achieve financial goals since that is what you ask for. And hey! I really can&#8217;t say no to you.</p>
<p>So there will be more videos on achieving goals financially as soon as I have looked into this topic a little more and detail down how I personally apply these strategies. I never want to give you anything I haven&#8217;t persoally tested and implemented. So please bare with me that this might take a little while.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ll give you updates on the progress every now and then. But before I know something works I will not recommend it and teach it to you.</p>
<p>Though, I have a request. Something I would want to ask you to do.</p>
<p>If and when I post and update I will share what I&#8217;m testing to implement and if you could try it out too and post your experiences on the result. Maybe this could be very beneficial for everyone.</p>
<p>I will do the ground work finding the strategies test it and share with you. You test it and share your results and maybe you occupation and free time activities and we could find some strategies works better for certain groups and such.</p>
<p>Take care and I&#8217;ll see you in the enxt video.</p>
<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WhoIsSvenWolf/~4/I_r6bjEbqsA" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
