      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hey there!</p>
<p>This is Sven Wolf from Sweden back on track after a long period of silence.</p>
<p>I know this is not appropriate to do since I am sharing some of my ideas on goal setting and how to stop procrastinating.</p>
<p>Well, let me tell you that I have not been lazy all this time.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve been busy building a coaching program and it has taken all free time I have had.</p>
<p>I have tried to stay connected on facebook with as many of you as possible but there are only 24h available each day so.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>But enough said about that. I&#8217;m back and noticed there has leaked in some spam in the older posts. But instead of going through them all I will continue where I was and perhaps re-write some of the posts that have gotten comments and feedback so that you will have a clean post to read.</p>
<p>Now, to my real agenda here. Watch this video down below and if you like it, please comment here and/or give me a thumbs up on youtube. Feel free to share with your friends on facebook and twitter (or any other social network)</p>
<p>I&#8217;ll catch you later!</p>
<p><object style="height: 390px; width: 640px"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/oBPxC1oDQ1A?version=3&#038;rel=0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always"><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/oBPxC1oDQ1A?version=3&#038;rel=0" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" allowScriptAccess="always" width="640" height="390"></object></p>
<p>Take care</p>
<p>//Sven</p>
